sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Proxy<br/>Istio Gateway
    participant API as vLLM OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine V1<br/>IPC/ZMQ
    participant PVC as Model Weights<br/>(PVC)
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,API: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request
    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS, Bearer API Key (optional)
    KServe->>API: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP
    API->>Engine: Process inference<br/>IPC (in-process or ZMQ)
    Engine->>PVC: Load model weights<br/>File I/O
    PVC-->>Engine: Model tensors
    Engine-->>API: Generated tokens
    API-->>KServe: JSON/SSE Response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    KServe-->>Client: Chat completion response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>TGIS: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP, Optional TLS
    TGIS->>Engine: Process inference<br/>IPC (in-process)
    Engine->>PVC: Load model weights<br/>File I/O
    PVC-->>Engine: Model tensors
    Engine-->>TGIS: Generated tokens
    TGIS-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Prom,API: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scrape
    Prom->>API: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    API-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over API,OTLP: Flow 4: Trace Export (Optional)
    API->>OTLP: Export traces<br/>gRPC 4317/TCP

    Note over Engine,HF: Flow 5: Model Download (Optional)
    Engine->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, HF Token
    HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts
